00:05:02,765 --> 00:05:04,765
to help us be more cinematic in our thinking

144
00:05:04,785 --> 00:05:06,025
and the way we're trying to tell stories

145
00:05:06,085 --> 00:05:08,766
is we've actually mirrored real-world lenses

146
00:05:08,846 --> 00:05:10,846
from an Alexa Prime camera package

147
00:05:10,866 --> 00:05:12,507
that you would find on a film set.

148
00:05:12,927 --> 00:05:15,087
This came from one of our incredibly talented animators,

149
00:05:15,107 --> 00:05:17,168
Josh Gridley, who had joined our team

150
00:05:17,708 --> 00:05:20,569
after leading a number of productions at third floor

151
00:05:20,609 --> 00:05:21,809
and working on film previs.

152
00:05:24,049 --> 00:05:25,390
So, now back to the story.

