225
00:08:13,111 --> 00:08:15,132
and all go over the scenes, provide feedback,

226
00:08:15,152 --> 00:08:17,053
a safe place to weigh in on what we're working on.

227
00:08:17,553 --> 00:08:21,902
This also helped us because we didn't have a singular person shooting them or editing them,

228
00:08:22,583 --> 00:08:24,006
so it helped us to remain connected.

229
00:08:24,367 --> 00:08:26,071
And the other benefit of jumping right into Preview is...

230
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,701
