259
00:09:30,311 --> 00:09:33,955
One of the other things we do in my opinion is we shoot scenes overall twice.

260
00:09:34,716 --> 00:09:36,958
The first pass is to get comprehension.

261
00:09:37,478 --> 00:09:39,900
