00:14:00,821 --> 00:14:05,883
To quote Walter Murch, an editor who worked on so many incredible films from Apocalypse Now to a number of other things,

364
00:14:06,264 --> 00:14:09,065
sound is a huge influence on people's attention.

365
00:14:09,506 --> 00:14:13,168
And with that in mind, we really try to make sure that our previews contains scores,

366
00:14:13,868 --> 00:14:17,870
sound effects, VFX, and really anything we can do to help sell our ideas better.

